Subject: Re: [T2] ethanol in vw engines

On Sun, 11 Nov 2007, John Leibowitz wrote:

> What about 50% Ethanol, or 80%?  What can one do to make their bus engine
> love the stuff?  I'm going into a rebuild right now and it'd be great to
> build it to Ethanol standards

Those will give you problems.  They need different jetting and may attack
components, even metal ones.  Exactly which components they will attack is
not obvious, you just have to keep an eye out for deterioration or
corrosion.
